2. UÅ¾raÅ¡ykite nagrinÄ—jamo a.d. pasiskirstymo ir tankio funkcijas (tolydÅ¾iu atveju) arba tikimybes (diskreÄiu atveju).

Pasiskirstymo funkcija (reikÄ—s paraÅ¡yti kÄ… reiÅ¡kia kiekviena raidÄ—): \[ F(x) = \frac{1}{1 + e^{-\frac{(x - \mu)}{\sigma}}} \]

Tankio funkcija (reikÄ—s paraÅ¡yti kÄ… reiÅ¡kia kiekviena raidÄ—): \[ f(x) = \frac{\sigma^{-1} e^{(x-\mu)/\sigma}}{(1 + e^{(x-\mu)/\sigma})^2} \]

library(maxLik)
## Warning: package 'maxLik' was built under R version 4.4.3
## Loading required package: miscTools

## Please cite the 'maxLik' package as:
## Henningsen, Arne and Toomet, Ott (2011). maxLik: A package for maximum likelihood estimation in R. Computational Statistics 26(3), 443-458. DOI 10.1007/s00180-010-0217-1.
## 
## If you have questions, suggestions, or comments regarding the 'maxLik' package, please use a forum or 'tracker' at maxLik's R-Forge site:
## https://r-forge.r-project.org/projects/maxlik/
logLikFun <- function(param) {
  location <- param[1]
  scale <- param[2]
  sum(dlogis(x1, location = location,
            scale = scale, log = TRUE))
}
mle <- maxLik(logLik = logLikFun,
              start = c(location = 0, scale = 1))
